```

### Running Jesse Backend
The API server provides routes for the dashboard:
```bash
# Stop any running process
pkill -f "jesse run"

# Start Jesse from bot directory (not jesse/)
cd /Users/salehmir/codes/jesse/dev-jesse/bot
